If I understood well, you extracted a 3.0 M4 build on top of an existing 2.1.1
install directory. 

You must extract Eclipse install to an empty directory. You don't need to do
that just to keep using the same workspace, because workspace and install
directories are independent. See how to use the -data command line option:
